title: Kendall Jenner flashes her butt (again) in lacy two-piece
text:
Published October 11, 2015 Facebook 0 Twitter 0 Email Print October 9, 2015. Cara Delevingne (L) and Kendall Jenner attend Eva Cavalli's birthday party at One Mayfair in London,England. (David M. Benett/Getty Images)
She may not have the most famous butt in the Kardashian family, but that doesn't stop Kendall Jenner from flaunting it.
The 19-year-old model bared her booty at a fancy masquerade ball held in honor of designer Roberto Cavalli's wife, Eva, on Friday at One Mayfair in London.
Getty Images WATCH: Kendall Jenner Poses Topless: 'I'm Washing Away My Sins'
Jenner looked very chic, wearing a navy bralette and a sheer lace skirt over high-waisted briefs -- which hardly covered her backside. She topped off the look with a velvet blazer.
